Predict output of following program

 

#include <stdio.h>



int fun(int n)

{

    if (n == 4)

       return n;

    else return 2*fun(n+1);

}





int main()

{

   printf("%d ", fun(2));

   return 0;

}



A
4
B
8
C
16
D
Runtime Error
Explanation
Fun(2) = 2 * Fun(3) and Fun(3) = 2 * Fun(4) ....(i)

Fun(4) = 4 ......(ii)

From equation (i) and (ii),

Fun(2) = 2 * 2 * Fun(4)

Fun(2) = 2 * 2 * 4

Fun(2) = 16. 



So, C is the correct answer
